  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To non-invasively estimate the alveolar surface area of the lungs of prematurely born infants&#xD;
      by taking measurements of oxygen and carbon dioxide and utilizing functional morphometry.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
